{
  "stem": "3666.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at one day in the middle of the night, they banged on our door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother came to the door and begged and begged and begged to leave us alone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was not so much worried about herself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was worried about my aunt and me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mostly about my aunt, but somehow about me, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, a lot of rape went on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were looting a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some Russians gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then at night, you didn't know what they were going to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- it was-- we went through a hard time, even after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother started to announce to people that she knows how to sew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she would get little jobs here and there, and they would give her food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was there that we spoke to other people who were also liberated in Torun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got some kind of communication from another city-- the city was Lodz-- that there is a much larger population of Jews there, that they are sort of congregating there, and that it might be a better idea to go where there are more Jews, with-- where you can touch base with other survivors and register [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as a survivor.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few months I think, a few months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] My mother found a little place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, we shared it with other survivors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were several families in one apartment, but at least you had some privacy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, it was there where she made a lot of contacts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She used to go every single day to the Judenrat, like to an office, a central office, to see if maybe my brother or my father showed up.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
